info.name: Dexter 8 light gunmetal cube floor lamp
info.description:
A real show stopper design statement made up of ajoined cubes that create fantastic shadow effect across your room.

Dimensions: Height 130cm, width 22cm
Composition:Steel, Glass
Bulb requirement:10W Max G4 Halogen Capsule Bulb (included), product compatible for dimmer
Self assembly requirements:no
Care Instructions: wipe clean with a soft dry cloth
